      <title>法国政府称提高电力税不会影响消费者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/french-government-says-raising-power-tax-won-t-hit-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国表示，拟议的电力税增加不会损害大多数家庭的利益，因为该国计划投入 606 亿欧元（663 亿美元）来解决公共财政问题并重建投资者信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/french-government-says-raising-power-tax-won-t-hit-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 12:52:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储 11 月不降息将“令人尴尬”：奥斯卡奖得主 Tchir</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-11/-embarrassing-if-fed-doesn-t-cut-in-academy-s-tchir-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Academy Securities 宏观策略主管 Peter Tchir 表示，如果美联储 11 月不降息，那将是“令人尴尬的”。他进一步补充说，美联储可能会降息 25 个基点，因为第四季度可能会出现一轮通胀。他在彭博简报中与 Dani Burger 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-11/-embarrassing-if-fed-doesn-t-cut-in-academy-s-tchir-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 12:46:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克银行利润可能因最低准备金率上调而受到冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/bank-profits-may-take-a-hit-from-czech-minimum-reserve-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了降低自身成本，捷克央行将所谓的最低准备金要求提高了一倍，此举可能会导致银行减少放贷并面临利润下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/bank-profits-may-take-a-hit-from-czech-minimum-reserve-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 09:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
